divs: Sighting DetailsI was out walking my dog ,i was just admiring how clear the sky was.When i looked up overtop of my house i saw an grey egg-shaped object at first i thought it was a balloon .then i saw that it was moving really fast across the sky . By the time i could get my phone out and snap two pictures it was gone . im trying to upload them but my phone is not working right. If anyone else has seen this i would like to know.
Summary: i was walking my dog looked up overtop pf my house and saw an object i got two pics on my phone and then it was gone.it moved really fast across the sky
